[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1668[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          where would you put the discomfort right
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1669[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          now?
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1670[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1671[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Patient: constant since I woke up. maybe a 5 or 6
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1672[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          out of 10.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1673[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1674[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Bot:     Does the pressure spread anywhere, like to
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1675[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          your arm, jaw, neck, or back?
