[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1710[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1711[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Bot:     Please wake her up and call 911 together.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1712[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          While you wait for the ambulance, sit
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1713[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          upright in a comfortable position. Don't
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1714[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          try to drive yourself. If you have aspirin
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1715[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          in the house and you're not allergic to it,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1716[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          the standard guidance for this situation is
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1717[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          to chew one regular aspirin (325 mg) or
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1718[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          four baby aspirin (81 mg each), but only if
