[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2032[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - [HL7 FHIR MedicationStatement Resource](https://www.hl7.org/fhir/medicationstatement.html): the FHIR resource for current-medication retrieval
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2033[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - [HL7 FHIR AllergyIntolerance Resource](https://www.hl7.org/fhir/allergyintolerance.html): the FHIR resource for allergy retrieval
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2034[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - [HL7 FHIR Encounter Resource](https://www.hl7.org/fhir/encounter.html): the FHIR resource for visit-history retrieval
